{{zh-forms|[[和尚打伞，无法无天]]|[[和尚]][[打]][[傘]]，[[無法無天]]}}
==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: (like a bald) monk holding up an umbrella - no (respect for) law<ref>law [[法紀|法(紀)]] and hair [[頭髮|(頭)髮]] are [[homophone]]s in Chinese.</ref> and order<ref>[[天]] literally means sky, but it is also short for [[天理]] (heavenly justice).</ref>.

===Idiom ([[歇後語]])===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' héshàng dǎ sǎn wúfǎwútiān)
# no respect for law and order; unruly

